snippet.title: Rocks and Ravens
snippet.description:
rocks and ravens is a short puzzle game inspired by haiku and Japanese logic puzzles like Sudoku.

It takes 5 to 10 minutes to complete. For the best experience, play with headphones and a cup of tea. 

Hope you enjoy!

play the game: https://playfulbacon.itch.io/rocks-and-ravens

watch every other video:
https://coconut-with-friends.itch.io
https://gamejolt.com/@CoconutWithFriends
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMtJ0WRGHgjIIsREZz69pYg
